function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idActor) == "spider_adult" then
		table.insert(tSpiders, idActor)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	if #tSpiders > 0 then
		for i, idSpider in pairs(tSpiders) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpider) then
				idChosenSpider = idSpider
				
				Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idChosenSpider, "DRV_MonsterSpawn_Spider")
				
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idChosenSpider, false)
				
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(idChosenSpider, idJumpLoc, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, false)
				Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idChosenSpider, idLootCorpse)
				Hydra.QActorPower(idChosenSpider, S_ANIM_SPIDER_MOUNT)
				
				Hydra.EventSend("Spider_Found")
				
				break
			end
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idLootCorpseCover, 0.5)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idCorpse, S_PWR_BURST)
	
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFX)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if idActorKilled == idChosenSpider then
		Hydra.EventSend("Spider Killed")
	end
end

function Start(szGroup)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idCorpse)
	--Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idLootCorpse, idCorpse)
	Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idCorpse, S_ANIM_HOST_MOUNT, S_ANIM_HOST_IDLE)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idCorpse, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLootCorpseCover) then
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idLootCorpseCover, 0.5)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idCorpse, S_PWR_BURST)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idFX)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idLootCorpseCover, 0.5)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idCorpse, S_PWR_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFX)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idOperate, false)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idBubble, 0.5)
end
